casebody.data:
Phillips, Respondent, v. Selchow et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. March 3, 1891.)

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

G. R. Hawes, for appellants. I. Levy, for respondent.

Mo opinion. Appeal from fifth district court. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
